Our favorite heroes in a half shell are back, but is this reimagined version of the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles worth the price of admission? Join us as we give our in-depth thoughts on the latest entry in the TMNT franchise; Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem. Whether you are cool, rude, or a party dude, you don't want to miss this spoilerific recap and review all about Leonardo, Raphael, Michaelangelo, and Donatello! Cowabunga! If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

